 Version 2.1 from 05-25-95
        Fixed troubles during config file reading.
        When compiling only net's segment first node excluded from list.
        Fixed.
        Add environment setting in CTL file such as in T-Mail. For format
        see T-Mail manual.
        Now asking on exit from T-Node. You can disable this option via
        NOASK command.
        Now T-NODE.CTL searching not in current directory, but on the path
        where T-NODE.EXE located. You can place T-NODE.EXE on Your paths -
